---
import MainLayout from "../layouts/MainLayout.astro";

const baseUrl = import.meta.env.BASE_URL;
---

<MainLayout
  title="About Bright Horizon | Technology Growth Partner"
  description="Bright Horizon is a trusted technology growth partner for businesses in South Africa. Over a decade of IT delivery, cloud hosting, Odoo ERP, automation, and digital transformation."
>
<section class="soft-gradient border-b border-[#1F7A63]/10">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6 py-20">
    <div class="mb-5 inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full border border-[#C79C49]/40 bg-[#C79C49]/10 px-4 py-1.5">
      <span class="h-1.5 w-1.5 shrink-0 rounded-full bg-[#c79c49]"></span>
      <span class="text-[0.7rem] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-[#6A4917]">Trusted Technology Partner</span>
    </div>
    <h1 class="animate-fade-up text-4xl font-bold text-[#145A46] md:text-5xl">Built to Help Businesses Grow</h1>
    <div class="mt-5 h-0.5 w-14 rounded-full" style="background: linear-gradient(90deg, #c79c49, rgba(199,156,73,0.15));"></div>
    <p class="animate-fade-up animate-delay-1 mt-5 max-w-3xl text-lg text-[#1A1A1A]/80">
      We are a technology growth partner for modern businesses — delivering cloud hosting, business systems, automation, and IT strategy that produces results you can measure.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6 py-16">
  <div class="grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-3">
    <article class="section-shell animate-fade-up p-8 md:col-span-2">
      <h2 class="mb-3 text-2xl font-semibold text-[#145A46]">Our Story</h2>
      <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed text-[#1A1A1A]/85">
        Bright Horizon was built on a simple conviction: businesses deserve technology that actually works for them — not against their budget or capacity. Led by an IT professional with over a decade of hands-on delivery across enterprise systems, cloud infrastructure, and digital transformation, we bring real-world experience to every engagement.
      </p>
      <p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-relaxed text-[#1A1A1A]/85">
        We've helped businesses reduce operational costs, go live on Odoo ERP, migrate to the cloud, automate manual processes, and build the digital foundation they need to compete and grow confidently.
      </p>
    </article>
    <article class="section-shell animate-fade-up animate-delay-1 p-8">
      <h2 class="mb-3 text-2xl font-semibold text-[#145A46]">Our Mission</h2>
      <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed text-[#1A1A1A]/85">
        To be the technology growth partner that businesses trust — delivering practical, scalable, and cost-effective solutions with a long-term commitment to your success.
      </p>
      <div class="mt-4 space-y-2">
        <div class="flex items-start gap-2.5"><span class="mt-1.5 h-1.5 w-1.5 shrink-0 rounded-full bg-[#c79c49]"></span><p class="text-sm text-[#1A1A1A]/75">Business outcomes over technology features</p></div>
        <div class="flex items-start gap-2.5"><span class="mt-1.5 h-1.5 w-1.5 shrink-0 rounded-full bg-[#c79c49]"></span><p class="text-sm text-[#1A1A1A]/75">Execution over advice alone</p></div>
        <div class="flex items-start gap-2.5"><span class="mt-1.5 h-1.5 w-1.5 shrink-0 rounded-full bg-[#c79c49]"></span><p class="text-sm text-[#1A1A1A]/75">Long-term partnership over one-time delivery</p></div>
      </div>
    </article>
    <article class="section-shell animate-fade-up animate-delay-2 p-8">
      <h2 class="mb-3 text-2xl font-semibold text-[#145A46]">Who We Serve</h2>
      <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed text-[#1A1A1A]/85">
        We work with SMEs, growing businesses, and enterprises across South Africa and beyond — from retail and professional services to logistics, hospitality, and manufacturing.
      </p>
      <p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-relaxed text-[#1A1A1A]/85">
        Whether you're a 5-person startup or a 200-person operation, we design solutions that fit your reality and grow with your ambition.
      </p>
    </article>
    <article class="section-shell animate-fade-up animate-delay-3 p-8 md:col-span-2">
      <h2 class="mb-3 text-2xl font-semibold text-[#145A46]">How We Work</h2>
      <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed text-[#1A1A1A]/85">
        We start every engagement with a structured discovery — understanding your goals, constraints, and current systems before recommending anything. Then we design, build, and deliver with clear milestones, transparent communication, and ongoing support.
      </p>
      <p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-relaxed text-[#1A1A1A]/85">
        You won't get generic advice or over-engineered solutions. You'll get a focused team that understands business as well as it understands technology — and is invested in getting it right.
      </p>
    </article>
    <article class="section-shell animate-fade-up animate-delay-4 p-8 md:col-span-3">
      <h2 class="mb-3 text-2xl font-semibold text-[#145A46]">Multi-Cloud Expertise</h2>
      <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed text-[#1A1A1A]/85">
        We are cloud-agnostic — meaning we recommend the right platform for your business needs, not the one we're contracted to sell. Our team is experienced across AWS, Azure, Google Cloud, and Oracle Cloud, ensuring you always get the best fit for your workload, budget, and scalability goals.
      </p>
      <div class="mt-4 flex flex-wrap gap-2">
        <span class="rounded-full border border-[#C79C49]/40 bg-[#0E3D35]/8 px-3 py-1 text-xs font-semibold text-[#145A46]">Amazon Web Services (AWS)</span>
        <span class="rounded-full border border-[#C79C49]/40 bg-[#0E3D35]/8 px-3 py-1 text-xs font-semibold text-[#145A46]">Microsoft Azure</span>
        <span class="rounded-full border border-[#C79C49]/40 bg-[#0E3D35]/8 px-3 py-1 text-xs font-semibold text-[#145A46]">Google Cloud</span>
        <span class="rounded-full border border-[#C79C49]/40 bg-[#0E3D35]/8 px-3 py-1 text-xs font-semibold text-[#145A46]">Oracle Cloud (OCI)</span>
      </div>
    </article>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6 pb-20">
  <div class="section-shell animate-fade-up p-10 text-center">
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold text-[#145A46]">Ready to Grow Your Business With Technology?</h2>
    <p class="mx-auto mt-3 max-w-2xl text-sm text-[#1A1A1A]/80">
      Book a discovery call or reach out directly. No obligation — just a real conversation about your goals and how we can help.
    </p>
    <div class="mt-7 flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-3">
      <a
        href="https://www.brighthorizon.co.za/contact/"
        target="_blank" rel="noreferrer"
        class="btn-primary btn-shine inline-flex rounded-full px-6 py-3 text-sm font-semibold"
      >
        Book a Consultation
      </a>
      <a
        href={`${baseUrl}contact`}
        class="inline-flex rounded-full border border-[#1F7A63]/35 px-6 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-[#145A46] transition hover:bg-[#1F7A63]/8"
      >
        Contact Us
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
</MainLayout>